<li class='cover' id='bookCover_81980'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/81980.America_s_Great_Depression"><img alt="America&#39;s Great Depression" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1568753869l/81980._SX98_.jpg" />
